            <dd><p class="normalContent">I am an undergraduate student majoring in Physics, driven by a deep fascination for unraveling the mysteries of the natural world. My passion for understanding the fundamental principles that govern the universe has guided my academic journey. With a solid foundation in linear algebra, calculus, group theory, classical mechanics and quantum mechanics, I have developed strong analytical and problem-solving skills through coursework and hands-on laboratory experiences. I aspire to contribute to cutting-edge research, drive innovation, and collaborate with fellow scientists to push the boundaries of human knowledge.</p></dd>

